abstract: >-
  A distributed honeypot intelligence platform that combines LLM-powered
  adaptive honeypots with reinforcement learning, automated SIEM rule
  generation (Suricata, Sigma, YARA), ML-based anomaly detection, and
  C2/covert channel detection. Processes 55M+ attack events from 22K+
  unique attacker IPs across 122 countries.
